display_long_description:
Tempo Travelers is free to play with co-op, single player and multiplayer party games packed into one mega fun game.
 
 
# **Break the Sound Barrier**
 
A unique movement style to move crazy fast.
 
Glide and fly at mach-speeds in an ever growing open world.
 
Track your speeds and become the fastest in the park!
 
 
# **FIRE SKINS**
 
Grab sick heads, jackets and boots from the Drip Shop.
 
1843 combinations possible. Mix and match parts to create your own style.
 
Find Tazo - the newest Tempo in the shop. Higher agility. More control.
 
 
# **Fun Mini Games with Many Levels**
 
Play infinitely with more mini game levels on the way:
 
- **Mach & Cheese** - speedrunning through a cheese track.
 
- **Tomato League** – fast paced 2v2 ball battle.
 
- **District M** – rhythm dreamworlds for solo play.
 
- **Scar City** – dominate the track and bump others off it.
 
Win to earn Fame, rare skins, and park-wide status. Fame System coming soon!
 
 
# **Enter the Arena. Become a Legend.**
 
Climb leaderboards. Win community tournaments.
 
Unlock trails, trophies, and legendary cosmetics that show you’re a top Traveler.
 
 
# **The Park Never Sleeps**
 
The world updates every week. New Tempos drop. Zones evolve. Secrets emerge.
 
Join live events on Discord and shape the future of the Park.
 
👉 Join more Travelers now: discord.gg/TempoVR
